        %p
          The framework will find all
          %code select
          elements and automatically enhance them into select menus, no need to apply a
          %code data-role
          attribute. To prevent the automatic enhancement of a select, add
          %code data-role="none"
          attribute to the
          = succeed "." do
            %code select
